This is a fork of https://sourceforge.net/projects/kudu/ (2013-03-22)

Kudu is a Gtk+ and OpenGL powered animation package, which relies moslty on skeletal animation and has an interface loosely based on the style of Wings3D.

License: GNU General Public License version 2.0 (GPLv2)


Kudu Animator 0.1.2
===================

Welcome and thanks for downloading Kudu!

Please see the file NEWS for info on this release.

Kudu is currently in pre-alpha stage.
Please don't expect full blown functionality and
hassle free operation. Feel free to make suggestions,
bug-reports and even (if you are a coder) patch
contributions. - This is a work in progress.


Installing Kudu:
================
For installation notes, please see the file INSTALL.
- Not applicable in the case of a binary release.


